text: Carlos Palavecino (born 19 February 1975) is an Argentine rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
